enitor. Finally, we find that the non-exploding models eventually evolve\ninto compact inner configurations that experience a quasi-periodic spiral SASI\nmode. We otherwise see little evidence of the SASI in the exploding models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 Sep 2019 20:44:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 15 Nov 2019 16:25:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-08"}
