igma^-$ light has a small effect on Bloch walls because $\\sigma^-$\nonly switches down spins up and once the spins already point up, there is no\nmajor effect.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 Sep 2019 22:36:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 9 Feb 2020 02:19:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-11"}
